trans-unit.source: Represents an ASP.NET trace message and any associated data.
trans-unit.target: Representerer sporingsmeldingen for ASP.NET og alle tilhørende data.

trans-unit.source: The TraceContextRecord object encapsulates the trace message, category, any associated <xref:System.Exception>, and whether the trace record was written by the <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Objektet TraceContextRecord innkapsler sporingsmeldingen, kategori alle tilknyttede <xref:System.Exception>, og om oppføringen sporingen ble skrevet med den <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: Every call to the <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Write%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName> methods generates a TraceContextRecord object that is added to the <xref:System.Web.TraceContextEventArgs.TraceRecords%2A?displayProperty=fullName> messages collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvert kall til den <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Write%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoder genererer en TraceContextRecord-objektet som legges til i <xref:System.Web.TraceContextEventArgs.TraceRecords%2A?displayProperty=fullName>meldinger samlingen.</xref:System.Web.TraceContextEventArgs.TraceRecords%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Write%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can access the collection of records by handling the <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.TraceFinished> event.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til samlingen av poster ved behandling av <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.TraceFinished>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.TraceContext.TraceFinished>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.TraceContextRecord"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.TraceContextRecord"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Every call to the <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Write%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName> methods generates a <xref:System.Web.TraceContextRecord> object that is added to the <xref:System.Web.TraceContextEventArgs.TraceRecords%2A?displayProperty=fullName> messages collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvert kall til den <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Write%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoder genererer en <xref:System.Web.TraceContextRecord>objektet som legges til i <xref:System.Web.TraceContextEventArgs.TraceRecords%2A?displayProperty=fullName>meldinger samlingen.</xref:System.Web.TraceContextEventArgs.TraceRecords%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.TraceContextRecord> </xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Write%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A> method call sets the <xref:System.Web.TraceContextRecord.IsWarning%2A> property to `true`, while the <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Write%2A> method calls set it to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A>metoden kall angir den <xref:System.Web.TraceContextRecord.IsWarning%2A>egenskapen `true`, mens den <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Write%2A>metodekall Sett den til `false`.</xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Write%2A> </xref:System.Web.TraceContextRecord.IsWarning%2A> </xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A>

trans-unit.source: The trace category that receives the message.
trans-unit.target: Sporingen kategorien som mottar meldingen.

trans-unit.source: The trace message.
trans-unit.target: Trace-melding.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the method associated with the <xref href="System.Web.TraceContextRecord"></xref> is the <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn*> method;<xref uid="langword_csharp_ false" name=" false" href=""></xref> if the tracing method is the <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Write*> method.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis metoden som er tilknyttet den <xref href="System.Web.TraceContextRecord"> </xref> er den <> </> *> metoden;<xref uid="langword_csharp_ false" name=" false" href=""> </xref> hvis metoden sporing av <> </> *> metoden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Exception> object that contains additional error information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Exception>objekt som inneholder mer feilinformasjon.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: Gets the user-defined category for the trace record.
trans-unit.target: Henter den brukerdefinerte kategorien før sporingen.

trans-unit.source: The category is used to better organize trace messages into recognizable groups, but can be any string.
trans-unit.target: Kategorien brukes til å organisere bedre Sporingsmeldinger i gjenkjennes grupper, men kan være en streng.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.TraceContext> class uses <xref:System.String.Empty?displayProperty=fullName> as its default category for methods that take only a `message` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.TraceContext>klasse bruker <xref:System.String.Empty?displayProperty=fullName>den standard kategori for metoder som tar bare et `message` parameteren.</xref:System.String.Empty?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.TraceContext>

trans-unit.source: The default category for ASP.NET, which writes several trace records when tracing is enabled, is "aspx.page".
trans-unit.target: Standardkategori for ASP.NET som skriver flere poster for sporingen når sporing er aktivert, er "aspx.page".

trans-unit.source: A string that represents a category for the trace record.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer en kategori for trace-post.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref:System.Exception> associated with the trace record, if one is available.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref:System.Exception>tilknyttet trace-posten hvis det er tilgjengelig.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: You can include an exception in a trace record if you are using tracing to debug an application or troubleshoot error and exception handling.
trans-unit.target: Du kan inkludere et unntak i en Sporingsoppføring Hvis du bruker sporing feilsøker et program eller feilsøking av feilen og unntaksbehandling.

trans-unit.source: The ErrorInfo property is `null` when the trace record is associated with one of the <xref:System.Web.TraceContext> methods that does not have an explicit `errorInfo` parameter or no exception is provided.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ErrorInfo er `null` når trace-oppføringen er knyttet til en av de <xref:System.Web.TraceContext>metoder som ikke har en eksplisitt `errorInfo` parameteren eller ingen unntaket er angitt.</xref:System.Web.TraceContext>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Exception> associated with the trace record, if one exists, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Exception>tilknyttet trace-posten hvis det finnes en eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the trace record is associated with a <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method call.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om oppføringen sporingen er knyttet til en <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName> metodekallet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Web.TraceContextRecord"></xref> is associated with the <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn*> method call; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref href="System.Web.TraceContextRecord"> </xref> er knyttet til den <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn*>metodekall; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the user-defined trace message.
trans-unit.target: Henter sporingsmeldingen brukerdefinerte.

trans-unit.source: The message can be any string, and is used to write detailed tracing information.
trans-unit.target: Meldingen kan være en streng, og brukes til å skrive detaljert sporingsinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: It corresponds to the message parameter that is passed to the <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Write%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName> methods.
trans-unit.target: Det samsvarer med meldingen-parameteren som sendes til den <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Write%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og <xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoder.</xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Warn%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.TraceContext.Write%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The information can be run-time values, messages to orient you and guide you through a program's execution, or other diagnostic data.
trans-unit.target: Informasjonen kan være kjøretid verdier, meldinger for å forstå du og veiledning for kjøring av et program eller andre diagnosedata.

trans-unit.source: A string that represents a message for the trace record.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer en melding før sporingen.
